OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fsunny spells, then clear spells
OL,7,Fovernight, with showers, the showers
OL,8,Fbecoming less frequent but still
OL,9,Foccasionally heavy. Touch of frost
OL,10,Fpossible in sheltered spots, but
OL,11,Fbreezy near coasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FAnother rather cold day with
OL,14,Fa mix of sunny spells and showers, the
OL,15,Fshowers tending to become less heavy
OL,16,Fthrough the afternoon and evening.
OL,17,FFresh to strong northerly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
