OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FShowers
OL,6,Fand northerly winds ease from west
OL,7,Fthrough Friday. Bright start Saturday
OL,8,Fcloud and rain edging east in
OL,9,Fafternoon. Morning rain Sunday then
OL,10,Fsunny spells and showers in afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
